    narr:narration """This hub gathers how *resonant framing* gets used — the rhetorical and structural devices that make dense thinking land. The load-bearing structural claims sit under `broader`: [density inversion at scale](narr:Narrative_DensityInversionAtScale) reframes dense thinkers' communication liability as an asset, and [verbatim-quote integration](narr:StyleObs_VerbatimQuoteIntegration) tracks a register where founder voice interrupts analytical prose (witnessed Mar→Jun 2026). Around these cluster a dense field of metaphor observations attached `related`: validation-as-vision-test ([eye-chart micro-telltales](narr:StyleObs_BetterAorB), [phoropter eye exam](narr:StyleObs_Optometrist)); reframing metaphors ([gold mines for AI](narr:StyleObs_GoldMineMetaphor), [repo-as-gift](narr:StyleObs_GiftMetaphor)); opacity and stakes ([gods of Olympus](narr:StyleObs_GodsMetaphor), [burning away](narr:StyleObs_BurningAwayMetaphor)); and grounding analogies ([consultant interview](narr:StyleObs_ConsultantInterviewAnalogy), [a design collaborator's brand consulting](narr:StyleObs_StructurallyIdentical), [religion-as-living-system](narr:StyleObs_ReligionAnalogy), [brain personification](narr:StyleObs_BrainPersonification)). One child breaks the rhetorical-device pattern entirely: [armor coming off](narr:Obs_ArmorComingOff) — a raw moment of mutual vulnerability, not a framing technique.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DensityInversionAtScale> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ArmorComingOff> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BetterAorB> ;
